<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278964>
    dc:description "FIGURES 40 – 48. Gogoltilla chichikovi gen. et sp. nov. 40. Female, habitus, dorsal view; 41. Male holotype, habitus, dorsal view; 42. Female, habitus, lateral view; 43. Male holotype, habitus, lateral view; 44 - 47. Male genitalia: dorsal view (left), ventral view (middle left), lateral view with penis valve removed (middle right), and lateral view of penis valve (right); 48. Male mandible, lateral external view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278964/files/figure.png" ;
